                    <div>⌨️ T - Technology tree</div>
                    <div>⌨️ Space - End turn</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="panel-section">
                <div class="panel-header">Victory Progress</div>
                <div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8;">
                    <div>🏛️ Control Capitals: <span id="capitals-controlled">1/4</span></div>
